      "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review+1\n\nI think this patch is fine as-is.\n\nI think it useful IMHO that the configure check and BuildRequires serve two different purposes.  BuildRequires enforces what we want for our RPM packages to include for end-users, while the configure check is for developer builds, or if the end-user is building and does not have all of the packages installed.",
